import React from 'react'; import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper } from '@mui/material'; const ShiftTable = ({ shifts }) => { return ( Location Date Start Time End Time Map Staff Gender Original Message Date Received Time Received Coordinator Assigned To Status {shifts.map((shift, index) => ( {shift.location} {shift.date} {shift.startTime} {shift.endTime} {shift.mapStaff} {shift.gender} {shift.originalMessage} {shift.dateReceived} {shift.timeReceived} {shift.coordinator} {shift.assignedTo} {shift.status} ))}
); }; export default ShiftTable;
